description:
The story follows Kohane Hatoya, a 1st year high school student who is a bit clumsy and scared of heights but who has a very bubbly and outgoing personality. Kohane decides to join the cheerleading club to try to make friends and overcome her weaknesses.

(Source: Crunchyroll)

[Wiki (jp)](https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/志茂文彦) | [Wiki (en)](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fumihiko_Shimo)

Noted for writing the scripts for Kyoto Animation's anime adaptations of Key visual novels.

Began his career as a production assistant on [Grave of the Fireflies](https://anilist.co/anime/578/), but switched to writing right after.
**Takashi Yoshizawa** is a Japanese producer and animation producer.

Assistant planner at Houbunsha.

_Note: Not to be confused with the [Capcom employee](https://anilist.co/staff/237972/)._
**Akito Takahashi** is a publicity producer working for Toho.

[Website](https://www.tateki.net/) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/TatekiKobayashi)

Tateki Kobayashi is a singer-songwriter, lyricist, composer, and music producer. Graduated from Kindai University.
__Keiji Oota__ is a Japanese producer and animation planner. Managing Director at Toho.
